quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,"Allah woondirii keneeli jarotooɗi leydi ndin !"
  51,2,"Mi woondirii kadi duule ronndotooɗe toɓo tiiɗngo !"
  51,3,"Mi woondirii kadi laaɗe dogirayɗe ka maayo ɗen no newori !"
  51,4,"E malaykaaji peccooji ko Alla yamiri yo fecce ko e fiyakuuji jiyaaɓe."
  51,5,"Ko Alla fodata on ko e hasbeede e yoɓeede ko goongo mbo alah jeddi."
  51,6,"Haasbeede ko ko wonat nyande darngo alah e sago."
  51,7,"Allah woondirii kammu labaangu tagu jom ɗate ngun."
  51,8,"Pellet, onon yimɓe Makka ɓee, hiɗon e konngol piyondirngol : nde wonnde wi'on : Alqur'aana ko mbilewu, nde wonnde kadi wi'on : ko nde gimi, ma wi'on kadi nde wonnde: Muhammadu ko mbileejo, e wonnde goo wi'on : ko yimoowo."
  51,9,"Hino yiltee e gomɗingol Alqur'aana e Annabiijo on (yo o his) kala firlitaaɗo e anndal Allah, e gomɗinal ngal; anndugol Mo wonnde onɗon gomɗintaa, ko ɗum waɗi si O firlitaa."
  51,10,"Ɓee fenuɓe e hoore Alqur'aana e Annabiijo maɓɓe on fow ɓe huɗaama."
  51,11,"Ɓen yooliiɓe e majjere, welsindiiɓe fii galle laakara ɗen."
  51,12,"Hiɓe lamndoo : ko honnde woni Ñalaande njoɓdi kuuɗe? Hara non ɓe alaa gollannde nde !"
  51,13,"Allah jaaboo lamndal maɓɓe ngal : ko Ñalaande nde ɓe leptoytee ka Yiite."
  51,14,"Ɓe wi'ane : meeɗee non lepte mon ɗen ; ko ɗum woni ko hawjiraynoɗon kon, waɗton jalnori, tuma jertintenoɗon."
  51,15,"Pellet ɓeen hulirɓe Joomi mum en ɗoftaade jamirooje Makka, e reenaade kaɗaaɗe Makka ñande darngo hoɓe e jardeeji e caalli dogooji."
  51,16,"Jaggatnooɓe ko Alla okkataɓe e njoɓdi teddundi, ɓe pellet ko adii ndii njoɓdi hoɓe moƴƴinatno golle ka aduna."
  51,17,"Hoɓe njuulatno jemma, ɓe ɗaanatanooko si wonah setta."
  51,18,"E saanga ndoogu hoɓe toro yaafeede bakkatuuji mum en ummorde ka Alla."
  51,19,"Ina e jawle mum en he hakke-hoɓe ngattoo heen- yimɓe ñaagatooɓe e ɓe ñaagataako,yimɓe haɗiraaɓe arsuko e kala sabaabu."
  51,20,"E nder leydi ko Alla waɗi ko e hendi ummaade e tule haa e maaje e caalli e leɗɗe e puɗi e kulle, ko dallillaaji mbaawko Alla wonande yananaaɓe wonde ko Alla woni takɗo mbaadinɗo."
  51,21,"Ina e nder pittaali mon - onon aade en- dallillaaji kollirooji mbaawko Alla, mbela on ndaaratah ngam teska ɗon?"
  51,22,"Ina nder kammu arsuko mon aduna, ina e hembo ko podante ɗon e moƴƴe e bonannde."
  51,23,"Mi woondirii Jom kammu e leydi, pellet ummital ko goongo mbo alah sikke e mum, hono no sikke waasi wonde e haala mon saanga nde kaalaton."
  51,24,"Mbela arii e ma -Aan Nulaaɗo- yeewtere hoɗɓe Ibraahiima jeyaaɓe e malaykaaji, ɓe Alla teddini."
  51,25,"Ndeɓe naati e makko, ɓe mbi*ni mbo salaaman: Ibraahiima ruttiɓe salminaandu, nduun woni salaam, O maaki e fittaandu makko: ɓe ko yimɓe ɓe nganndaaka."
  51,26,"O fayi to yimɓe makko e mbaadi cuuiindi, o addori toon ngaari payndi, sabu o sikkuno koɓe yimɓe."
  51,27,"O ɓanni ɓe ngaari ndi, o haaldi e maɓɓe e newuya: mbela on ñaamatah?"
  51,28,"Nede ɓe waasno ñaamde o so*i e fittaandu makko he kulol, ɓe paami ɗuum, ɓe lelnir ɓernde makko wiide taa hulu, minen komin nulaaɓe ummaade ka Alla, ɓe kabri mbo ko welata mbo, ɗuum woni ma o heɓ keewɗo ganndal, ko oon woni Ishaaqa."
  51,29,"Nde jom suudu makko nani o wela wela o ari homo wulla ngam weltaare, o hellii yeeso makko, o wii hombo haawa: mbela nayeeja na jibina, te kanko ko o dimara."
  51,30,"Malaykaaji ɗi mbi* imbo ko min kabru ma ko woni ko Joom ma daali, ko O daali ko noon ruttetaake, ko Kanko woni ñeeñuɗo e tagu Makko e hoddiro Makko, ganndo tagu Makko e ko nafataɓe."
  51,31,"Annabi Ibraahiima maaki Malaa'iɓe ɓen : ko honɗum woni fii mon? E ko faanditiɗon?"
  51,32,"Malaa'ika'en jaabii mo wonnde : menen, Allah neli men e yimɓe bomɓe ɓen faggitotooɓe kuuɗe bonɗe."
  51,33,"Fii yo men accitu e maɓɓe, kaaƴe iwɗe e loope juɗaaɗe"
  51,34,"Maandiniraaɗe ka Joomi maa an Ibraahiima, wurtaaɗe e yawtooɓe keeri Allah ɓen, fantinooɓe yeddugol Mo ngol."
  51,35,"Men yaltini taho kala gomɗimɓe wonunooɓe e saare yimɓe Luutu ɓen, fii wata lepte bomɓe ɓen hawru e maɓɓe."
  51,36,"Men tawaano e nden saare, si wanaa suudu juulɓe wooturu, ndun le ko suudu ɓeynguure Luutu nden (yo o his)."
  51,37,"men acci e nden saare yimɓe Luutu, batteeji lepte ɗen, ko holla wonnde ɗe yanuno e maɓɓe, wona waajitorɗum kala huloowo lepte muusuɗe ɗen yanunooɗe e maɓɓe, ontigi hula waɗugol sugu kuuɗe maɓɓe ɗen, fii daɗugol ɗen lepte."
  51,38,"Men acci kadi maande e Muusaa, tuma nde Men nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wonndude e hujjaaji ɓannguɗi, wonannde kala huloowo e lepte muusuɗe ɗen."
  51,39,"Kono Fir'awna ɗuurni fawaade e cemmbe e konu makko fow salii goonga, o wi'i Muusaa : ko mbilɗotooɗo yimɓe maa hara feetuɗo."
  51,40,"Men nanngi mo kanko e koneeli makko ɗin fow, Men weddii ɓe ka maayo, ɓe yoolii ɓe halkii, tawde Fir'awna ko feliraaɗo fennugol mo ngol nodditoo reweteeɗo."
  51,41,"Men acci kadi maande e 'Adi'en, yimɓe Huudu ɓen, wonannde kala huloowo lepte muusuɗe ɗen, tuma nde Men wurtunoo e maɓɓe henndu ndu ardaa e toɓo, ndu worgintaa leɗɗe ndu aldaa kadi e barke."
  51,42,"Ndu accataa hay wonkii maa jawdi ekw e kon ko ndu arani, si wanaa ndu muncay fii mun, ndu waɗta ɗum wano rappunde sariinde."
  51,43,"Men waɗi kadi maande e Samuuda'en, yimɓe Annabi Saalih ɓen, wonannde kala huloowo lepte muusuɗe ɗen, tuma nde ɓe wi'ananoo : awa dakmitoree nguurndam mon ɗam, ado lajal mon gal timmude."
  51,44,"Ɓe townitanii yawmiroore Joomi maɓɓe gomɗingol e ɗoftagol Mo ngol, haacaango lepte ngon nanngi ɓe, tawi hiɓe ƴeewa ko ɗum jippotoo kon. Tawde ɓe kammbirano lepte ɗen, balɗe tati ado ɗe jippaade."
  51,45,"Ɓe waawaano duñugol lepte ɗen gaay e maɓɓe, ɓe heɓaano kadi feere faabeede."
  51,46,"Gomɗii kadi Men halkiriino yimɓe Nuuhu ɓen ado ɓee jantaaɓe ɗoo, yoolagol. Pellet, ɓen ko yimɓe yaltunooɓe e ɗoftaare Allah, waɗi si ɓe hanndi e lepte Makko ɗen."
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Men mahir ngu doole Amen, Men ɗiggini ɗum. Pellet, ko Men yaanooɓe cebe mammba."
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Men weertiranndi hoɗooɓe ɓen, wano ndaɗɗundi maɓɓe. Men moƴƴii weertan ɓe ndi."
  51,49,"E kala huunde, Men tagii noone ɗiɗi: wano deyel e gorel, kammu e leydi, njodrndi e maayo; balajo'o on waajitoray gootaagu Allah taguɗo ɗin On, teskoɗon fii kattal Makko ngal."
  51,50,"Dogee lepte Allah ɗen, yaccoron e mbarjaari Makko ndin, ɗoftaare e anngal yeddugol Mo. Min, wonannde on onon ɓee yimɓe, ko mi jertinoowo e lepte Makko ɗen, ɓannguɗo jertinol."
  51,51,"Wata on waɗde e Allah reweteeɗo goo ko rewon. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi ɓannguɗo jertinol."
  51,52,"nKo wano yimɓe Makko ɓen fenniri nii, mofte adinooɓe ɓen fennirnoo. Nulaaɗo Allah araali e ɓen, si wanaa ɓe wi'ay mo : ko mbileejo maa feetuɗo!"
  51,53,"Hara heeferɓe adinooɓe ɓen yamondirno e sakkitiiɓe ɓen e ngol fennugol Nulaaɓe? Oo'o woye. Ko woni kon, ko bewre renndiniɓe e mum."
  51,54,"An Nulaaɗo, selu ɓee fennooɓe, a wonaa felniiɗo. Ko pellet, a yottinii ko nulaɗaa kon e maɓɓe."
  51,55,"Haɗataa si a selii ɓe, waajoraa ɓe anndintinaa ɓe; tawde waajagol anndina ngol, hino nafa gomɗimɓe Allah ɓen."
  51,56,"Mi tagiraali jinna e yimɓe, si wanaa fii yo ɓe rewan Min tun. Wanaa dey fii yo ɓe waddam e goɗɗum goo."
  51,57,"Mi ɗaɓɓiraa ɓe arsike; Mi ɗaɓɓiraa ɓe yo ɓe ñamminam."
  51,58,"Pellet, ko Allah woni arsikoowo jeyaaɓe ɓen, fow no hatonjini e arsike Makko On, Kanko Jom cemmbe tiiɗuɗe ɗe huunde foolataa. Denndangal jinna e yimɓe ko cemmbe Makko ɗen yankinanii."
  51,59,"Haray hino woodani tooñirɓe ko'e mun ɓen fennugol ma, an Nulaaɗo, geɓal e lepte, yeru geɓal nanndo maɓɓe'en adinooɓe ɓen. Ɗum no happanaa lajal, wata ɓe ɗaɓɓiram yaccinangol ɓe ɗum ado happu mun on."
  51,60,"Halkaare woodanii ɓen yedduɓe Allah, ɓe fenni Nulaaɗo Makko on, e nden Ñalaande Darngal nde ɓe kammbiranaa yanugol lepte ɗen e maɓɓe."
